text:
I had a good time staying in the airstream.  Renee and Thomas were quick and responsive to my questions.

Not having a bathroom was a bit of an adventure at night, since you need to go to the main house for that.

Overall I had a great time and would recommend this place.  Next time I would stay in the house, because that seemed like a better value and it has a nice aesthetic too.
title: Mod Retro Airstream Heart of Austin
